  "industry_note": "UNS R30021 / Stellite 21 / Co-28Cr-6Mo + 0.25C — cast cobalt-base wear-resistant alloy. ASTM F75 의 wrought 와 동일 chem (Stellite 21 은 cast version). σy 510 / UTS 730 / El 14% (cast). Tmax 760°C. 우수한 wear (galling/sliding 저항), 고온 oxidation 저항. 의료 임플란트 (cast hip femoral stem, ASTM F75 = Stellite 21), industrial 베어링, hard-facing overlay (welded onto valve seat), engine valve face. 일반 Stellite 6 (Co-28Cr-4W-1.1C) 대비 lower wear but higher impact.",
